Series creator Vince Gilligan and star Aaron Paul join the Mythbusters team to scrutinise the science of the hit television show, Breaking Bad. First up, Adam and Jamie take on a bathtub blowout, because according to the program, hydrofluoric acid could chew through organic matter, a bathtub, the floor and the ceiling. Meanwhile, Kari, Tory and Grant break bad with a mercury fulminate fable, which is based on a scene where Walter White decimates an entire room with a fistful of crystal. 


